        "description": "<p>This plugin prevents the 404 error on author pages when the author has no posts.</p>\n<p>It is published under the GPL 2 licence (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-2.0.txt).</p>\n<p>The original idea was taken from the the &#8220;List Authors&#8221; plugin here: http://guff.szub.net/source/custom-list-authors.php</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload <code>/show-authors-without-posts/show-authors-without-posts.php</code> to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>That&#8217;s all.</li>\n</ol>\n"
